      • create

        public static JsoParserBuilder create()
        Instantiates a new clean-slate JsoParserBuilder object.

        This is equivalent to simply calling new JsoParserBuilder().

        Note that this method creates a builder initialized to all default settings, whereas builder() copies the settings of the object called on.

        Returns:
        A new JsoParserBuilder object.
